Package: mfou
Title: Simulation, Inference, Forecasting, and Spillover Analysis with the Multivariate Fractional Ornstein-Uhlenbeck Process and the Multivariate Fractional Brownian Motion
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ranieri", "Dugo", , "dugoranieri@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Collection of functions that allow modeling multivariate time series data using the Multivariate Fractional Ornstein-Uhlenbeck process and the Multivariate Fractional Brownian Motion. These allow the simulation of the processes, the identification of its parameters from discrete observations (data), forecasting the process h-step ahead, and performing spillover analyses. Also, companion package to Dugo, Giorgio, Pigato (2024a, 2024b).
